dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Shows southeastern states plus part of Cuba and Bahamas. Watermark. Included in Wytfliet's "Descriptionis Ptolemaicae Augmentum" which was published in 1597. 1 map; 22 x 27 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
